<L>__{exterior chimera with murphy continuous day}
<A>__{as the ship dips lower, the rushing water forms an eddy that pulls at murphy. murphy struggles, too heavy to resist as he is pulled closer and closer to the sucking maw that is the smokestack's opening. the ship sinks further and murphy is pulled to the edge of the stack. he frantically grabs for something to hold on to, without success, until he is finally pulled into the smoke stack and sucked into the bowels of the ship by the rushing water.}
